<subSubSection id="51B965115628FFFD53C9FF3FFD4FFF1A" box="[136,719,158,185]" pageId="12" pageNumber="21" type="nomenclature">
<paragraph id="191C369A5628FFFD53C9FF3FFD4FFF1A" blockId="12.[136,719,158,185]" box="[136,719,158,185]" pageId="12" pageNumber="21">
<heading id="425481F65628FFFD53C9FF3FFD4FFF1A" bold="true" box="[136,719,158,185]" fontSize="11" level="1" pageId="12" pageNumber="21" reason="1">
<emphasis id="2BD7EA885628FFFD53C9FF3FFD4FFF1A" bold="true" box="[136,719,158,185]" pageId="12" pageNumber="21">
Key to the species of the 
<taxonomicName id="DEA34D195628FFFD52EFFF3FFD00FF1B" authorityName="Gussone ex Lojacono" authorityYear="1903" box="[430,640,158,185]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Centaurea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="12" pageNumber="21" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="aeolica">
<emphasis id="2BD7EA885628FFFD52EFFF3FFD00FF1B" bold="true" box="[430,640,158,185]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="21">Centaurea aeolica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group
</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="51B965115628FFFD53C9FF7DFA2BFE18" pageId="12" pageNumber="21" type="key">
<keyStep id="A2572E3F5628FFFD53C9FF7DFA2BFEE5" pageId="12" pageNumber="21">
<paragraph id="191C369A5628FFFD53C9FF7DFA2BFEAF" blockId="12.[136,1452,219,443]" pageId="12" pageNumber="21">
<keyLead id="A25295AF5628FFFD53C9FF7DFA2BFEAF" pageId="12" pageNumber="21">
1. Basal leaves usually lyrate, with lacinia apex obtuse to rounded, phyllaries pale brown with blackish apex, with 1 to 2–5 teeth..... ....................................................................................................................................................................................... 
<taxonomicName id="DEA34D195628FFFD5665FF58FA2BFEAF" authorityName="Beguinot" authorityYear="1905" baseAuthorityName="Fiori &amp; Beguinot" box="[1316,1451,248,270]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Centaurea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="12" pageNumber="21" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pandataria">
<emphasis id="2BD7EA885628FFFD5665FF58FA2BFEAF" box="[1316,1451,248,270]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="21">C. pandataria</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="191C369A5628FFFD53C9FEB4FA2BFEE5" blockId="12.[136,1452,219,443]" pageId="12" pageNumber="21">
<keyLead id="A25295AF5628FFFD53C9FEB4FA2BFEE5" pageId="12" pageNumber="21">– Basal leaves 1–2-pinnatisect, never lyrate, with lacinia apex acute, phyllaries whitish to straw-coloured, with 7–15 teeth or fimbriae...............................................................................................................................................................................................2</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
<keyStep id="A2572E3F5628FFFD53C9FEEEFA2BFE18" pageId="12" pageNumber="21">
<paragraph id="191C369A5628FFFD53C9FEEEFA2BFE22" blockId="12.[136,1452,219,443]" pageId="12" pageNumber="21">
<keyLead id="A25295AF5628FFFD53C9FEEEFA2BFE22" pageId="12" pageNumber="21">
2. Tomentum greenish-grey, leaves 1–2-pinnatisect, with laciniae loosely inserted, phyllaries 7-nerved, appendages denticulate with teeth 
<quantity id="DE5B9B7F5628FFFD5246FECAFE06FE23" box="[263,390,363,385]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.75" metricValueMax="3.0" metricValueMin="0.5" pageId="12" pageNumber="21" unit="mm" value="0.175" valueMax="0.3" valueMin="0.05">0.05–0.3 mm</quantity>
long....................................................................................................................................................... 
<taxonomicName id="DEA34D195628FFFD5609FECDFA2BFE22" authorityName="Gussone ex Lojacono" authorityYear="1903" box="[1352,1451,363,385]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Centaurea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="12" pageNumber="21" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="aeolica">
<emphasis id="2BD7EA885628FFFD5609FECDFA2BFE22" box="[1352,1451,363,385]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="21">C. aeolica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="191C369A5628FFFD53C9FE28FA2BFE18" blockId="12.[136,1452,219,443]" pageId="12" pageNumber="21">
<keyLead id="A25295AF5628FFFD53C9FE28FA2BFE18" pageId="12" pageNumber="21">
– Tomentum whitish-grey, leaves 1-pinnatisect (rarely 2-pinnatisect), with laciniae densely inserted, phyllaries 5-nerved, appendages fimbriate with fimbriae up to 
<quantity id="DE5B9B7F5628FFFD52AEFE04FDB8FE18" box="[495,568,421,443]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.5" pageId="12" pageNumber="21" unit="mm" value="1.5">1.5 mm</quantity>
long ................................................................................................................... 
<taxonomicName id="DEA34D195628FFFD5666FE04FA2BFE18" box="[1319,1451,421,442]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Centaurea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="12" pageNumber="21" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="phalacrica">
<emphasis id="2BD7EA885628FFFD5666FE04FA2BFE18" box="[1319,1451,421,442]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="21">C. phalacrica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
</subSubSection>
